{"tid":2315951,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"女星罕露隱乳見客！一轉身「前V後U」半全裸設計辣翻","createTime":"2020-12-07T13:31:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-07T13:48:11.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"bf31f75280d0cc8bf2342a13bd4ad17b8fda351d","tid":2315951,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T13:31:27.000Z","msg":"少女時代於2007年出道，2017年10月，Tiffany、秀英及徐玄出走SM娛樂，不再續約，形同單飛不解散。而各自有不同出路的女孩們，也逐漸在所屬領域站穩腳步，秀英轉型成演員，近日還與任時完、申世景有新戲要上，沒想到6日晚間出席MAMA頒獎典禮時，反而超火辣的半裸穿著讓粉絲直噴鼻血。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/12/07/2922779-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F12%2F07%2F2922779-PH.jpg&h=ec2e312f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲秀英擁有模特兒身材。（圖／翻攝自秀英IG）<br />\n<br />\n秀英近日受邀出席頒獎典禮，170公分的她再踩5公分高的高跟鞋，整個人看起來更加修長，她換上一套絲綢材質的深V開衩禮服，不僅前V後U，背部更是以半全裸的方式出現，下半身則是露出超長漫畫腿，在媒體拍攝區時，還一個大轉身，果然讓鎂光燈閃不停。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/12/07/2922780-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F12%2F07%2F2922780-PH.jpg&h=e5f790db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼▲秀英出席MAMA典禮，辣穿大紅色禮服。（圖／翻攝自秀英IG）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/12/07/2922778-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F12%2F07%2F2922778-PH.jpg&h=2da0eeef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有趣的是，這次秀英交往多年的男友鄭敬淏也是一前一後上台頒獎，粉絲笑喊「如果看到自己女友穿這麼辣，誰都會受不了吧！」連與鄭敬淏一同頒獎的柳演錫一上台就意有所指開玩笑「為什麼今天是兩個男人上台？」似乎是暗指應該要找秀英跟鄭敬淏一起比較有看頭。"},{"pid":"3e7c69f797a42c346dc77c5cba6784326955a276","tid":2315951,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T13:31:56.000Z","msg":"痴線架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6392dfde71a644fc3cb77eb254fcc21ff568c1ba","tid":2315951,"uid":3405,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T13:34:01.000Z","msg":"美腿呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82be5c60c6622872651bea864d473fa7855d3356","tid":2315951,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3e7c69f797a42c346dc77c5cba6784326955a276","tid":2315951,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T13:31:56.000Z","msg":"痴線架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T13:36:44.000Z","msg":"SNSD<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1871971fa0bc30609d12a94af5e151d5c921264b","tid":2315951,"uid":224479,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T13:47:12.000Z","msg":"twice世界第一"},{"pid":"026a39e960c6bfa3a7a1d80b152c9c4247154e33","tid":2315951,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1871971fa0bc30609d12a94af5e151d5c921264b","tid":2315951,"uid":224479,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T13:47:12.000Z","msg":"twice世界第一"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T13:47:50.000Z","msg":"twice宇宙第一la<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6157df93e48211431091324d77f120ddcbb9899","tid":2315951,"uid":219225,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T13:48:11.000Z","msg":"老女人。。"}]}